T2 weighted sequences, sensitized to diffusion by gradients. A sequence is a configuration of radiofrequency pulses and gradients that result in images with a particular appearance. T2 sequences without modification indicate fluid as white, muscle as gray, fat as white, gray matter as gray and white matter is darkish compared to gray matter.
